cat << EOF
hyperpen is an Xorg input driver for Aiptek HyperPen RS232-based tablet
devices. For the USB-based HyperPens, please see the "aiptek" driver.

The hyperpen driver functions as a pointer input device, and may be used
as the X server's core pointer.

SUPPORTED HARDWARE
This driver supports the Aiptek HyperPen 6000, and Tevion MD 9310
tablets.
EOF
